snippet.title: Maze Mice - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam! https://MazeMice.com/
Maze Mice is a bullet heaven roguelite where time only moves when you move. Collect dots, level up, choose upgrades, and avoid cats. All at your own pace.

Pixel art by specialmin64
Music by Vincent Colavita
Sound effects by Gabriel Gallardo-Alarcon
End screen art by Kevin Fagaragan
Text effects by Laragh Walsh

https://TrampolineTales.com/
